node.text:
Hi 👶🏻 baby Tasha, let’s talk to each other at eye level! Trying to impress mini-me no. 2 with a baby firefly pose, not sure how I fared. 😂 .
Swipe left to #throwback to Sept 2018 of the same pose I did with the elder one (20 months old then) who was clearly unimpressed 😅. Things mummies do during the #circuitbreakersg to get the attention of their kids!😅
.
#7monthsold #sgunited #stayhomeforsg
@thechillmom hahahhaha thanks for the encouraging words, my pretty mama😘😘!! I hope my bb felt the same!!!🤣
This is damn amazing you look so chill. Please teach me how to get into this hahaha
Awe lovely pics 💗💗💗 and amazing firefly variation 😍😍😍
That's a cool pose! And kids that cooperate with your photo taking!
I m impressed for sure hee
I'm impressed tho!!!😍🙌💕 For them it's pretty normal haha!!
